Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, shoot, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't earn some Life before I reach the field...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, will you please stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.06,0:00:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any Magic or Trap Cards here that can recover your Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all I can do is fight against someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is anyone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, just stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you tell me that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tron, ever since I saw you for the first time at the evening festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't been able to shake off the fear that's been eating away at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.68,0:00:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm positive this man can step on those things precious to us and crush them without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'll stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron, I won't let you reach Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you must really think highly of Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh my… The ones who chose Jungle Field were…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the former Operation Committee member Droite and the mysterious boy Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Field Magic has been implanted in all four fields of the Finals,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}which have given them distinctive characteristics!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, what will this Jungle Field offer-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What the heck happened?!\N - In the middle of such an important moment, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What an unthinkable mistake!\N I am most sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please fix this as soon as possible, staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way I can allow\N our guests to see this match, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:02:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too late for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:03:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8000 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(597,506)}"Number 54: Tron vs Droite - Allure of the Death Butterfly!\N The Life-Threatening Jungle Field!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a crafty one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what trick you use, I will defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,507)}Here in this Jungle Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,512)}If a player does not Summon, Special Summon, or set from their hand while
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this Field Magic is activated, they take 1000 points of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You came here knowing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one who set Traps on my Coaster route in order to lure me into this jungle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really went to some great lengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first turn belongs to me! My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card,\N Phantasmal Dance of the Confusing Butterflies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I play this card when there is a Field Magic in play,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon the Level 4 or lower Phantom Butterfly Assassins, Morpho and Swallowtail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourselves, Phantom Butterfly Assassins Morpho, Swallowtail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay the Level Four Morpho and Swallowtail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use these two Monsters to build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.40,0:04:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Photon Butterfly Assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Xyz right off the bat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:05:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I'll entertain you further with these three Continuous Magic Cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up first is Butterfly Charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the Field Spell, this Jungle Field will deal great damage to the player who has not Summoned or set a Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, I was listening before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, with Butterfly Charm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you Summon a Monster in Attack Mode that does not declare attack, it will be forcefully destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then all I have to do is attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second, Assassin Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster whose name does not contain “Assassin” attacks, it will be forcefully destroyed by this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then my Monsters will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The only fate awaiting your Monsters is destruction, regardless of what you try to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third, Death Butterfly's Invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to maintain this card once activated, I need to pay 2000 of my Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when a Monster on the field is destroyed, it will inflict 1500 damage to the controlling player!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I will receive damage if I don’t Summon a Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even if I manage to Summon one, it will be destroyed, and I will receive critical damage in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You use up 2000 of your Life in exchange for 1500 damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So that's why you raised your Life all the way up to 8000!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this combo’s operation, you will be engulfed by this jungle within three turns!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since that day, I have always...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My fellow young Duelists,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's painful... unbearable, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But thanks to that pain, the next generation of elite Duelists shall be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Trap, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-That's...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alright, the Ghost Lord is on a rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you wish to be rescued, you will need to win the Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I Summon Daybreaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go! Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don’t rely on others!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment you begin relying on others is the moment you lose sight of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I recall... that's Kaito's little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto, take a look. It's a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That might of yours that refuses to rely on anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It exists solely to protect your little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I see your smile, I can't help but think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even that smile... looks kind of sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.58,0:09:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Kaito protects Haruto, I will protect Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't rely on anyone else. I will fight on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All so I can see Kaito's smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means I must be a sacrifice for your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah man! It seems I'll be playing the buffoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The jungle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:09:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma! Hey, look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got caught by a terrifying trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three Magic Cards on Droite's field?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a combo using those three Continuous Magic Cards and the Field Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong one that forces the opponent to Summon a Monster, destroy it, then inflict damage to the player.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that powerful?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a way to get around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will triumph over love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Due to the Jungle Field, I have to Summon a Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I Summon it in Attack Position, your combo will activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, the correct response is…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The correct response is to set a Monster in face-down Defense Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I set one card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what now? Your combo won't activate if I set a Monster in Defense Mode, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot escape me in this jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.21,0:11:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, in order to keep Death Butterfly's Invitation, I will pay 2000 of my Life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Photon Assassin Butterfly's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By detaching one Overlay Unit, it can switch one Monster on the field from Defense Position to Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that Monster's Attack Power will drop 600 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heraldry Beast Aberconway was changed to Attack Position!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Assassin Butterfly, attack Aberconway!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butterfly Death Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of the Continuous Magic, Death Butterfly's Invitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the destroyed Monster's controller...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...takes 1500 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome, Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a Monster in face-down Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A flawless, perfect combo, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you meet Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cutting away your own Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.38,0:12:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no, cutting away your actual life in order to protect Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you thinking of Kaito to that extent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of your actions are what \Nwe refer to as the "power of love", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Love? Droite's doing this for Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, you're so thickheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.02,0:13:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the power of love, huh? It's kind of lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it now? Even if you play a Monster in Defense Mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be unable to escape from this combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn. Draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Heraldry Beast Bernard's Falcon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally prepared yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This moment you Summoned a Monster in Attack Mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the effect of the Continuous Magic, Butterfly Charm, will activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the Monsters on my opponent's field in Attack Mode must attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, I activate the effect of the Continuous Magic, Assassin's Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Monsters attack that don't have "Assassin" in their name, they are forcefully destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of the effect of Death Butterfly's Invitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you take 1500 damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.68,0:14:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Tron dude may really not be able to beat Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! Now my victory is assure-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice. {\i1}Very{\i0} nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "power of love" humans share.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to experience it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean your painful emotions overflowing with memories of Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sink my teeth into those memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card High Medallion Arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card allows me to conduct an Xyz Summon using two Heraldry Beasts with the same level from my Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.82,0:14:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to Xyz Summon with Monsters from the Graveyard!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay the Level Four Aberconway and Bernard’s Falcon from my Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use these two Monsters to build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Number 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heraldry King Genome Heriter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron's Number!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end my turn with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes no difference whether you played a Number! The next turn will determine the outcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you lay even one finger on Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the effect of Photon Butterfly Assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detach one Overlay Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It switches a Defense Monster into Attack Mode and reduces its Attack Power by 600 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excite Scales!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Butterfly Assassin attacks Heraldry King Genome Heriter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ends it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butterfly Death Dance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! If this gets through...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Genome Heriter's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By detaching one Overlay Unit, I can choose one of 3 effects!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will steal your Monster’s name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stole its name. Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Genome Heriter’s name changes to Photon Butterfly Assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, your Monster's lost its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what will happen if it's no longer an "Assassin".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll activate the effect of the Continuous Magic, Assassin Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When a Monster whose name does not contain "Assassin" attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the attack is negated and it's destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash to pieces, Miss Nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My combo's been broken...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, as per the effect of the Continuous Magic, Death Butterfly Invitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll take 1500 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean I can't defeat that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I just thought of something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:18:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll steal your memories from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... Droite's memories have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Tron's powers beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you fighting for Kaito's sake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta win... and go see Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't rely on others!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I won't rely on anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Moonlit Papillion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Flip Summon the Phantom Butterfly Assassin Ulysses I had set in reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay the Level Four Phantom Butterfly Assassin Ulysses and Moonlit Papillion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use these two Monsters to build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself! Photon Alexandra Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite... hasn't given up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the effect of Photon Alexandra Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detach all of her Overlay Units to send every Monster on the field to our hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,inflicting 500 points of damage to each player for each!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- A draw?!\N - A draw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.36,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butterfly Effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need my Life... nor my real one at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with the memories I hold of Kaito, I will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said for an insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings, your memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will become a delicious meal for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap, activate! Medallion Record!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It negates an effect that uses Overlay Units!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn... end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite! Stay with us!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! I don't want to forget... you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're flowing into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your consciousness... Your memories... Your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep inside me, Droite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I attack Photon Alexandra Queen with Photon Butterfly Assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butterfly Death Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the effect of Death Butterfly's Invitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite, you will journey to the land of amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.30,0:21:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of love aren't tasty {\i1}at all{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.59,0:21:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I'll eat {\i1}your{\i0} heart, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell that person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... remember me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.64,0:22:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's... Tron's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever... forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.29,0:23:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next battle takes place in the Space Field! The showdown between that Kaito and V will start!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:24:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, we learn the shocking truth from V.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His attacks won't get through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, V, and my dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.42,0:24:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did all the mysteries start here?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.67,0:24:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Galaxy Eyes Sealed?! The Cosmic Class Number Appears!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...really a Monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time we're gonna introduce Number 8, Heraldry King Genome Heriter!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a terrifying Monster with the ability to absorb the name of the opposing Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.86,0:24:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, did you forget my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.36,0:24:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, who are you again?
